title: AMAZING PARAMOUNT WORLD FULLY FURNISHED!!
posting_body: ['Welcome home to one of Miami’s most desired luxury towers, Paramount at Miami World Center.', 'This premium unit comes with a private foyer, 9 ft + ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows in the living spaces and bedrooms, west sunset views that capture beautiful afternoon lighting, and cityscape!', 'Expansive floor plan, high-end finishes/appliances, high end furnishings included, 2 bedrooms + Den, and 3 full bathrooms.', 'The Miami Paramount is a newer modern design building in the Downtown Miami Area and is known for its 5-star amenities compared to other luxury high rises in the area!', 'Resort Style Pools, fitness, boxing, yoga, music studios, basketball, tennis, massage/spa services for your indulgence', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
